added.title: Red Action to the Future
added.description: When Red Action is called to the future for an epic battle, Enid is unsure of what to do.

added.title: We Got Hacked
added.description: Dendy helps KO, Enid and Rad stop a glitch that threatens to take over the bodega.

added.title: The Guy
added.description: Gumball and Darwin put Anais' new friend, Josh, through a series of tests, to see if he's good enough for their sister. However, when the boys' extreme methods start freaking Josh out, he questions whether being Anais's friend is worth the trouble. So Gumball and Darwin end up having to convince Josh to give Anais a second chance.

added.title: The Detective
added.description: Anais arrives in the bedroom to find a messy crime-scene and her Daisy doll missing. She realizes Gumball and Darwin are the chief suspects. Following a series of clues is her only chance to track them down and her only hope of learning what happened to Daisy. But as the mystery unravels, it seems the culprits may have turned on each other.

added.title: The Nobody
added.description: Gumball and Darwin discover they have an uninvited house guest. Things keep going missing in the house, so it's up to Gumball and Darwin to find the culprit. They discover that a mysterious person has been secretly living in their home. Gumball and Darwin manage to turn this confused squatter into their mortal enemy . . .

added.title: The Knights
added.description: Gumball and Tobias compete for Penny's affection by putting on the lamest duel in history.

added.title: The Debt
added.description: Gumball resolves to save Mr Robinson's life during Elmore's Senior Talent Show.

added.title: Room for Ruby
added.description: Steven's Gem family continues to grow.

added.title: Super Watermelon Island
added.description: Steven finds out what happened to all those sentient watermelons he created.

added.title: Hit the Diamond
added.description: Steven and the Gems play an old fashioned game of baseball.

added.title: Friend Ship
added.description: The Crystal Gems explore an ancient Gem spaceship.

added.title: Steven's Lion
added.description: Steven makes friends with a magical lion, but can't quite tell why it likes him.

added.title: Cheer Up Pops
added.description: The guys want to cheer up Pops.

added.title: Marvolo the Wizard
added.description: Pops thinks that he's a wizard trapped in medieval times, and he wants to go back home.

added.title: Dumped at the Altar
added.description: The guys have to get Muscle Man married.

added.title: Inventor Mentor
added.description: Uncle Grandpa goes ti Italy to help a young girl who wants to be a great inventor.

added.title: Uncle Baseball
added.description: A failing little league team on the brink of giving up gets help from Uncle Grandpa and some Major League Baseball players.

added.title: Uncle Grandpa Runs for President
added.description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve run against one another in the RV presidential race.

added.title: Space Oddity
added.description: In the year 3021, the gang's intergalactic mission goes awry when a strange alien creature infiltrates their ship.

added.title: Super Alien Hero Buddy Adventures
added.description: Ben discovers his alien heroes have been ripped off by a lame cartoon and he is not happy. So he sets out to make things right.

added.title: Motel
added.description: Following an insect mishap Clarence's house needs to be fumigated forcing Mary, Chad, and Clarence into a motel. In the meantime, Clarence and Chad learn a bit about responsibility while Mary contemplates a life of letting go.

added.title: Clarence for President
added.description: It's school election time at Aberdale Elementary, and Jeff is once again determined to become Class President. However like previous years, he's unsuccessful in connecting with other kid. That is until he sees a shoe-in puppet President, the lovable Clarence!

added.title: The Boxcurse Children
added.description: Clarence, Jeff, and Sumo stumble upon a mysterious box. After they open it, some strange things begin to happen. Convinced they've unlocked a curse, they become determined to reverse it!

added.title: Ultimate Weapon
added.description: When Max finds out that part of an alien weapon has been unearthed in Texas, he becomes obsessed with finding it. In doing so, he leads Ben and Gwen on a wild adventure.

added.title: Benson Be Gone
added.description: Mordecai sees Pops naked and goes on a quest to unsee what he has seen.

added.title: The Chamber of Frozen Blades
added.description: In Ninja-mode, Finn and Jake break into Ice King's palace to catch him red-handed.

added.title: Ice Cream Hunt
added.description: Clarence enlists the help of his eccentric neighbor Larry to take the trio out for ice cream and the ride of their lives!

added.title: Grilled Cheese Deluxe
added.description: Mordecai and Rigby lie about being astronauts in order to cut in line at a restaurant.

added.title: The Alliance
added.description: As Fourarms, Ben works to thwart an armored truck robbery by a tough female gang leader named Joey, who delivers a disturbing message from Vilgax.

added.title: Dream Boat
added.description: Sumo devotes himself to the Sisyphean task of building a boat, defying the expectations of everyone in his life, including himself.

added.title: Ocean of Fear
added.description: Finn faces his biggest challenge yet...overcoming his fear of water.

added.title: Donny
added.description: In an attempt to save a village, Finn and Jake rehabilitate Donny the Ogre, who's a real jerk.

added.title: Rainy Day Daydream
added.description: Jake's imagination runs wild and Finn has to stop it before it kills them.

added.title: Vilgax Must Croak
added.description: Ben and Rook escort Vilgax to a maximum-security prison planet, but the Incurseans have other plans. (Introducing Eighteight.)

added.title: Finn Meets His Hero
added.description: Finn meets his adventuring role model, only to learn he's become a wuss in his old age.

added.title: The Frogs of War Part 1
added.description: The Incursean Armada, with the help of Dr. Psychobos, have invaded the Earth. (Reintroducing old Ben alien, BenMummy.)

added.title: Rules of Engagement
added.description: Princess Looma returns to claim Ben as her husband, and she's not going to let anyone stand in her way!  (Featuring Julie and Ship.)

added.title: Evil's Encore
added.description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

added.title: Food Around the Corner
added.description: Ben as Gravattack attempts to moderate a fragile peace treaty, but must endure the attacks of tiny alien fleas, which have inhabited his body.
